
# Directory colors for tomorrow-night-bright

# Term Section
TERM tmux
TERM screen
TERM xterm

# Attribute codes:
# 00=none 01=bold 04=underscore 05=blink 07=reverse 08=concealed
#
# Tomorrow night eighties theme:
# 45;45;45 Background
# 57;57;57 Current Line
# 81;81;81 Selection
# 204;204;204 Foreground
# 153;153;153 Comment
# 242;119;122 Red
# 249;145;87 Orange
# 255;204;102 Yellow
# 153;204;153 Green
# 102;204;204 Aqua
# 102;153;204 Blue
# 204;153;204 Purple

## Special files

NORMAL 38;2;204;204;204 # foreground
FILE 38;2;204;204;204 # foreground
RESET 0
DIR 38;2;102;153;204 # green
LINK 38;2;102;204;204 # aqua
FIFO 38;2;242;119;122 # red
SOCK 38;2;255;204;102 # yellow
BLK 48;2;102;153;204;38;2;204;204;204 # foreground on blue
CHR 48;2;102;153;204;38;2;204;204;204 # foreground on blue
ORPHAN 48;2;242;119;122;38;2;204;204;204 # foreground on red
EXEC 38;2;204;153;204 # purple

# MULTIHARDLINK 0 # regular file with more than one link
# SETUID # file that is setuid (u+s)
# SETGID # file that is setgid (g+s)
# CAPABILITY # file with capability
# STICKY # dir with the sticky bit set (+t) and not other-writable
# STICKY_OTHER_WRITABLE # dir that is sticky and other-writable (+t,o+w)
# OTHER_WRITABLE # dir that is other-writable (o+w) and not sticky
# DOOR

